Lindby Sofian hanging lamp, three-bulb, smoky grey
fields.description:
Three-bulb Sofian hanging lamp with a spherical smoked glass lampshade

Sofian is the perfect hanging light for the dining room as it is designed in a three-bulb, long shape and can thus provide extensive illumination of a table. Each of the three lampshades is almost spherical in shape and is made of glass, producing a very stylish look that can be combined with modern interiors. The surface of the lampshades is an attractive, slightly glossy smoky grey colour, which not only has a positive effect on the appearance of the hanging light, but also gives the light an extravagant touch and harmoniously underlines an atmospheric ambience.

fields.name: Karou hanging light, 5-bulb, stained grey
fields.description:
Attractive and imposing: Karou hanging light with three lampshades in a cage look

The Karou hanging light impresses with the slim lampshades made of stainless steel. The three lampshades in the hip cage look come in a subtle black and can be fitted with E27 bulbs. The bulbs are available separately. The striking Karou hanging light is 180 x 730 x 1,500 millimetres in size and is ideal for medium to large-sized rooms.

You can enhance a living room or dining room in the industrial or country style with the original Karou hanging light. This light source also looks great with a wide range of modern interiors.

fields.name: ELC Kalean LED ceiling spotlight, nickel, 4-bulb
fields.description:
Kalean four-bulb LED ceiling spotlight in nickel with GU10 bulbs

Kalean is perfect for a kitchen or a hall and provides a bright light in an appropriate way. Thanks to the LED technology, only a small amount of power is consumed when the ceiling spotlight is used. Therefore we can claim a good energy efficiency, which is very much in the spirit of a modern mindset. The silvery nickel finish underlines the modern overall effect of the four-bulb spotlight for installation on the ceiling. Each spotlight can be rotated and pivoted. This gives you enough suitable options for lighting that is adjusted to the situation.

fields.name: Linear pendant light Cintia with wood, 6-bulb
fields.description:
Innovative Cintia beam pendant light with six lamp heads

A dark, striking design shapes the look of the Cintia beam pendant light. The materials used include pine wood, steel and metal. A small, matt black wooden beam sits on the ceiling. Two cable-like struts run down from this beam at an angle and support a wide wooden beam. The cables are visibly randomly wound around this dark pine wood beam. They then hang down at different lengths and carry the six lamp heads. The sockets are also black and complete the colour scheme. The result is effective, bright lighting, so that the Cintia pendant light can be used in dark, rustic interiors with great results.

fields.name: Midway pendant light in black/copper 4-bulb round
fields.description:
Midway pendant light in black/copper 4-bulb round

Midway is fitted with GU10 LED bulbs, which are energy-saving and also shine at various levels of brightness - all you need is an external dimmer switch. The LED ceiling lamp combines an industrial style with an antique appearance. The industrial charm is largely owed to the mesh covers; whilst the rust finish is not just deceptively real, it also sparks a feeling of nostalgia in the onlooker, as you are led to believe that the light dates back several decades.
.

fields.name: Hanging light Emily in black, three-bulb
fields.description:
Frame-shaped Emily pendant light in open, box-shaped design

The Emily pendant light has a rectangular metal lampshade, which actually consists of a box-shaped frame. This creates the impression of a lampshade, although the open design provides a clear view of the three light bulbs. As such, the bulbs have a clear presence and form a visual component of the light. They should be chosen with care - so-called rustic bulbs, which now feature LED technology, have a nostalgic look and enhance the light.

The pendant lamp also embodies the ever-popular cage look, which impresses with its retro charm.

fields.name: Ticino - LED ceiling lamp, 3 bulbs
fields.description:
3-bulb LED ceiling lamp Ticino in an impressive design

Ticino is equipped with LED lamps which have a G9 base. This means not only that you get energy-saving light when you turn the ceiling lamp on, but also that it can be put into operation soon after installation because the light bulbs are included. Visually, Ticino produces a very modern impression, but also has a playful, dynamic look. This is not least caused by the metal bars being so artistically intertwined. In addition, the metal mesh spheres create a stylish appearance and result in an even light with a cosy character.

fields.name: Ceiling lamp Umma, semi-flush, grey
fields.description:
Slightly suspended Umma ceiling lamp with round fabric lampshade and impressive lasercut pattern

Umma looks great with modern interiors and has a relatively simple appearance thanks to its cylindrical shape. The fabric lampshade comes in white and features a stylish, lasercut perforated pattern. This looks great when the ceiling light is switched off, but looks especially atmospheric when the E14 light sources are switched on. Then the lighting looks like a small starry sky. And who doesn’t want to enjoy that effect within their own four walls?

The bottom of the ceiling light features a white fabric diffuser to produce evenly distributed lighting with a very homely effect. Meanwhile, the grey fabric design has a trendy look and can be ideally combined with different colours, including bright and bold shades.

fields.name: Pikka LED ceiling light with a white lampshade
fields.description:
Beautiful Pikka fabric ceiling light in white

The Pikka fabric ceiling light is operated by E27 LED lamps that are included in the product and keep power consumption at a low level. This is why the fabric ceiling light’s lampshade, installed onto the ceiling with a gap, looks so elegant, since it is precisely composed of two lampshades that have been effectively combined into one. The outer lampshade is transparent and made of organza fabric; the interior is made of firmer fabric. A white glass panel is fixed to the bottom of the inner lampshade, which distributes the light softly to give the room a homely feel.

fields.name: Marlo LED ceiling lamp white 3000 K round 25.2 cm
fields.description:
Marlo bathroom ceiling light with warm white LEDs

Simple in its design, but impressive in its performance, the modern Marlo ceiling light has a timeless, round frame and contains energy-efficient LED technology that reliably lights up the surrounding area with a pleasant, warm white light. The ceiling lamp lights up the room uniformly and evenly. Whether it is installed in the bathroom or in other moisture-prone rooms, Marlo is a useful light source for both the private sphere and the commercial sector.

fields.name: Lindby Flavi bathroom ceiling lamp, Ø 23 cm nickel
fields.description:
Round Flavi bathroom ceiling lamp with a satin nickel surround

This ceiling lamp has the IP code IP44, which is why it is intended for use in the bathroom. The lampshade is made of white glass that is surrounded by a metal ring with a satin nickel finish. The choice of bulb is at the consumer's discretion, as there are a number of different bulbs available for the E27 sockets.

fields.name: Extravagant Lisandra LED ceiling light
fields.description:
isandra LED ceiling light with glimmering crystal glass elements, can also be installed in bathrooms

The Lisandra LED ceiling light has a metal ceiling mount with a modern, glossy chrome surface. The light’s lampshade is made of partly-satinised glass with clear edges on the inside and on the outside. A gap between the mount and the glass plate is created thanks to four metal spacers. The hanging crystal elements, which reach through the middle of the lampshade, are visible in this area. The light is refracted by the teardrop crystal elements, thereby creating sparkling effects.

The integrated LED lamps have a warm white colour and are highly energy efficient as they achieve a luminous efficiency of 95 lumens per watt. They also stand out thanks to their exceptionally long lifetime, which, in this case, is 20,000 hours.

This Lisandra ceiling light is especially interesting for those who desire sophisticated and elegant lighting for the bathroom, as Lisandra can be used here without any concerns due to its IP rating of IP44, which gives it sufficient protection against dirt and water.

fields.name: Dimmable LED floor lamp Lilian, chintz lampshade
fields.description:
Stylish LED floor lamp Lilian with a chintz lampshade, dimmable

The LED floor lamp with its white chintz lampshade is energy-efficient, stylish and practical at the same time. The classic light is very easy to operate, not only by means of the pull switch, but also using the foot dimmer. The flexible alignment of the white lampshade is another highlight. The successful combination of matt and polished brass also makes the light into a real eye-catcher. The floor lamp Lilian attracts just as much attention in a tasteful reading corner as in the living room, the hall or the bedroom. The modern, puristic light can also be operated in an energy-efficient way and still emits a pleasant, cosy light. Due to its classic elegance, the floor lamp skilfully enhances the interior design concept. After all, it fits discreetly into a wide variety of interior design styles.

fields.name: Cream Natalia floor lamp, printing on the inside
fields.description:
Extraordinary floor lamp Natalia with a velvet textile lampshade

The unique retro charm of Natalia's high-quality floor lamp is only visible at second glance. After all, the cream-coloured velvet lampshade hides a sweet mystery. The interior print of the Natalia light reveals a striking retro pattern in green, brown, and orange, reminiscent of abstract flowers. The wooden tripod, which gives the floor lamp a safe stand with that special something, also fits harmoniously into the overall concept of this light. A transparent cable and foot switch allow you to operate the lamp easily and is an eye-catcher next to the sofa in the living room as well as a cosy light in a reading corner.

fields.name: Ruben floor lamp, black, three-bulb
fields.description:
Three-bulb Ruben floor lamp

The floor lamp comes with three E27 sockets that are surrounded by a black metal frame. They are mounted on three rods of different lengths, which end in gold-coloured brass detail at the top. The rods are attached side by side to the central strut of the metal frame.

The floor lamp is a real eye-catcher. It instantly attracts attention and is completely extraordinary from a purely visual point of view. In spite of the simple design, the arrangement of the light bulbs alone provides a playful touch. It is a feel-good light - the bulbs appear to sprout from the base like flowers and bring light to the dark.

Depending on the choice of light bulb (a warm white LED filament bulb is recommended), the floor lamp emits a lot of light and lights up the room with a cosy light.

A switch on the cable allows you to turn the floor lamp on and off without any problems.

fields.name: Rock salt lamp emits wellness light 3 kg
fields.description:
Pleasant salt lamp with a soothing glow

This crystal salt stone is unique in shape and size because it is a handmade natural product. It fits in anywhere as a decorative piece and its warm orange tone ensures a pleasant atmosphere. The light’s wooden base emphasises its natural look. The Rock salt lamp is available in various product versions. This lamp provides the right lighting for every room and every taste.

fields.name: Fabric table lamp Benjiro with an LED reading lamp
fields.description:
Round fabric table lamp Benjiro with an additional flexible reading arm

The round, white fabric lampshade on Benjiro provides lovely, comfortable lighting, which is perfect for cosy accent lighting in the evenings. Scattered lighting is no use for reading however, when you require more targeted lighting - as such, the fabric table lamp Benjiro also features an illuminating LED flexible arm, which can be rotated in any direction. Thus, you can get comfortable on the sofa and simply switch on the reading light when you want to read.

The two light sources can be switched on and off separately from one another and the switches are located near the bulb socket so that they are easily accessible.

fields.name: Lette LED table lamp with timer, battery-powered
fields.description:
Battery-powered LED table lamp Lette with integrated timer

The LED table lamp Lette is made of plastic and has an opal white colour. The lampshade is cylindrical and stands on a round base. From the base a handle leads in an arc around the lamp, which makes transport easier, because the lamp is not bound to any power source and can be taken everywhere flexibly. This is guaranteed by batteries, which are available separately. The integrated timer can be individually programmed and automatically switches the lamp on and off at the same time. Lette is ideal for decorative lighting or for accent lighting during cosy hours. The diffuse, warm white light emitted by it is gently distributed throughout the room, creating a cosy ambience.

fields.name: Lucande Ferda ceiling light for outdoors
fields.description:
Ferda ceiling light for outdoors

Sheltered outdoor areas, such as terraces or verandas, are suitable for the modern Ferda ceiling light. It emits a bright light from above and reliably illuminates the surrounding area. The bulb is protected from external weather conditions by a transparent glass cylinder. The body is made of robust aluminium, which makes the Ferda ceiling light versatile.

fields.name: Naira LED outdoor ceiling lamp, grey, with sensor
fields.description:
Grey Naira LED ceiling light with a white diffuser, seawater-resistant, IP65

Naira can be used anywhere outdoors and is also suitable for installation on the wall. The round design with the dark grey finish has a discreet and timeless appearance. The IP code IP65 promises a high level of protection for use outdoors, which means that it is easy to use the light for canopied building entrances or for terraces and balconies with an overhang. Feed-through wiring to other lights is possible. The body is robust and is made of plastic. It impresses with its seawater resistance, which means that the light can even be installed near salty bodies of water. A high impact resistance (IK06) is also guaranteed, which implies that the light is very robust - this is also a significant advantage outdoors.

Motion sensor data:

- Range 12 m/6 m

- Adjustable lighting duration: 5 s/90 s/5 mins/15 mins)

- Maximum installation height 6 m

- Detection angle 30°/150°

fields.name: Melzo practical LED outdoor wall light
fields.description:
The Melzo outdoor LED light – for wall or ceiling

The practical LED outdoor wall light Melzo can be installed outside as either a wall or ceiling light. Its modern and variable design also means it can be placed at ground level. The versatility of the light makes it a real all-rounder for outdoors. It provides sufficient light at any moment with its energy-saving and efficient LEDs, which illuminate the surrounding area glare-free with their warm white light.

fields.name: Buzzard myGarden - black outdoor wall lamp
fields.description:
Outdoor wall lamp Buzzard myGarden in the vintage style

The outdoor wall lamp Buzzard myGarden from Philips is a decorative light source for the fantastic illumination of the entrance, terrace etc. Made from matt black painted aluminium, it was designed in the shape of a lantern which hangs on a looped metal element on the wall mount. No light is swallowed by the clear glass lampshade, with the result that the light bulb used - either a traditional light bulb or an LED bulb - can emit its light unhindered in all directions. The use of an LED bulb in filament technology, which is not only very energy-efficient, but also extremely durable and also decorative and is shown to particular advantage in the clear lampshade, is particularly recommended.

fields.name: Abby LED outdoor wall light without sensor
fields.description:
Seawater-resistant Abby LED outdoor wall lamp with a dark grey finish, IP65

The Abby LED outdoor wall light is arranged at an incline and emits its light downwards. Thanks to the LED technology, the light output is high even though energy consumption is low. The body is robust and well sealed and can be used outdoors without any problems. Abby is also seawater-resistant and can even withstand the harsher climate near the sea, which means that you can enjoy this dark grey outdoor lamp for a long time.

- Impact resistance IK06

fields.name: Artu outdoor wall light with an antique look
fields.description:
Artu outdoor wall light: The large glass lampshade provides bright light

Like a relic from the past, the Artu outdoor wall light exudes antique flair in both its design and colour. It can be used to illuminate properties designed in the antique or maritime style. The hemispherical clear glass body provides brilliant bright light. The white gold colour of the metal underlines its antique look. Light bulb: 1 x 60 W max. E27. The light bulb is not included.

fields.name: Deck light Ceci 160-3L 10W in grey
fields.description:
Deck light Ceci 160-3L in grey with a replaceable LED bulb

The LED deck light is suitable for a variety of lighting purposes throughout the outdoor area. The warm white light of the LED bulb used shines through its three integrated light outlets and gently lights up the immediate vicinity.  

Ceci is made of synthetic resin in a robust, seawater-resistant design and can be traversed without any problems. The optimal light source for all areas on the property which are driven on.

- Made in Italy

- UV-resistant

- Impact-resistant

- Recyclable

fields.name: Paulmann LED solar recessed floor light Aron
fields.description: Durable LED solar deck light Aron with motion sensor The Aron recessed floor light from Paulmann offers practical orientation lighting for outdoor areas, which is completely independent of an external power supply or switching device. The angular, flat light can be installed flush with the paving. The housing with stainless steel frames and a plastic cover effectively protects the internal technology from water and mechanical loads up to 500 kg. The soft orientation light is activated by the integrated twilight sensor when daylight is waning. The motion detector detects approaching persons or vehicles at a distance of up to 1 m and provides the full LED functional light for 10 s when the "MODE" circuit is activated. The solar cells charge the 3.7 V 18650 battery for 8 hours during the day. The battery supplies Aron with energy for up to 12 hours.

fields.name: Suria-24 - round LED deck light, 24°
fields.description:
Robust Suria-24 LED deck light

The Suria-24 LED deck light is used to light up outdoor areas with a pleasantly warm white and particularly bright light. The light outlet ensures that the 24 W LED technology emits light at an angle of 24°. Due to its load bearing capacity of up to 1,000 kg, the deck light is perfect for driveways.

fields.name: Endura Flood sensor outdoor spotlight 840 DG
fields.description: Dark grey LED outdoor spotlight Endura Flood with sensor, light colour 4,000 K A compact design, energy-efficient, universal white lighting that provides enormous energy savings compared to halogen spotlights and uniform illumination thanks to a partially frosted tempered glass cover - these are the features of the Endura Flood Sensor LED outdoor spotlight. The LED outdoor spotlight for versatile use can be swivelled by up to 180° in its mounting bracket and is suitable for use in the temperature range from -10 to 40 °C. The IR daylight and motion sensor built into the spotlight can be adjusted to suit requirements. Data sensor: Detection angle 120°, detection range 2 to 9 metres (adjustable), daylight sensor detection threshold 20-2,000 lux (adjustable. The new LEDVANCE products, formerly known under the OSRAM brand name, combine the highest quality standards with modern design.

fields.name: XLED Home 2 XL - LED wall light with sensor
fields.description:
Innovative LED outdoor wall light XLED Home 2 XL with far-reaching light

The XLED Home 2 XL LED outdoor wall light made from UV-resistant plastic makes dark entrance areas or driveways a thing of the past, as the innovative LED technology and the integrated passive infrared sensor allow the light to provide light over a wide area, and precisely when it is required. Both the LED panel itself and the motion sensor can be variably adjusted, making the light a completely flexible lighting miracle. The LED lighting technology installed in the LED panel also scores points with a very long service life and an efficient power consumption.

fields.name: Emilio solar wall light with sensor and LEDs
fields.description:
LED solar wall light Emilio with a built-in sensor
The solar panel is located on the top of Emilio and offers plenty of space for the sunlight. As the day turns to night, the LED solar wall light begins to illuminate and it offers excellent orientation lighting for the garden. It can be also be affixed to a shed when there is no electricity connection nearby. The light shines downwards, and an integrated motion detector offers greater efficiency for the lighting. The detection range is between five and eight metres and the detection angle is 90°.

fields.name: Adem LED solar deco light, ethnic style, 30.5 cm
fields.description:
Brown LED solar decorative light Adem with a moon-shaped design

Finally, the garden is bathed in moonlight every night, as the Adem LED solar decorative light is in the shape of a crescent moon and adds an attractive eye-catching feature to the ambience of the outdoor area. The brown colour fades into the background so that the light emitted by the round body is the sole focus of attention.

Whilst the decorative light wraps the garden in its light in the evening and at night, it is charged during the day via a solar panel. It provides excellent lighting for benches, ponds etc. and shows them off decoratively.

fields.name: Fency - LED solar wall light in set of 3
fields.description:
Effective Fency solar LED wall light in a set of three
The round Fency solar wall light offers effective lighting. The light emitted by the LEDs shines through the rippled plastic cover to create ray of light below the light itself on the wall. The solar panel on the top of the light charges the NiMH batteries (3 x AA) during the day so that they can provide warm white LED lighting when darkness falls. The set of three solar lights illuminates the house façade for up to six hours, depending on the battery level.

fields.name: Filip LED solar light in graphite, ground spike
fields.description:
LED path light Filip with ground spike and solar module

Along paths in the entrance area or in the garden, the Filip LED path light is ideal for lighting and decoration. It is absolutely flexible and can be used anywhere without a power connection thanks to the integrated rechargeable battery, which is charged with energy from a solar panel in the top of the light. The solar light is ready for operation after 36 hours in the sun and then starts to light up automatically thanks to the integrated day/night sensor.

fields.name: E27 9 W 830 LED bulb, warm white
fields.description:
With its traditional light bulb shape and warm white luminous colour of 3,000 K, this LED bulb is suitable for use in living and office rooms and replaces a traditional 60 W light bulb.

The bulb is distinguished by its high efficiency and low energy consumption as well as a very long lifetime of up to 30,000 hours.

Additional characteristics are mercury-free production, a minimal start time (< 1 second - 100 brightness immediately) as well as low heat and low UV radiation.

fields.name: E27 LED rustic bulb 6 W 500 lm, amber 2,200 K
fields.description:
E27 LED rustic bulb with filament technology in decorative amber

This light bulb, with its traditional shape and amber-coloured glass, looks very decorative when placed in cage lights or open lights and will enhance any light.

The built-in LEDs offer filament technology and produce pleasant, cosy lighting for the living room or bedroom thanks to the very warm lighting (2,200 K).

fields.name: Filament LED bulb E27 7.5 W, warm white, dimmable
fields.description:
E27 7.5 W LED filament bulb with the best EEC A++

With a light output of 806 lumens, the LED bulb provides sufficient brightness and is a very energy-efficient replacement for conventional light bulbs of up to 60 watts.

fields.name: GU5.3 MR16 halogen bulb Decostar51 Standard 50W 36
fields.description:
GU5.3 MR16 50W 36° halogen bulb Decostar 51 - OSRAM

This cold light reflector bulb DECOSTAR 51 is the right solution, because it radiates the heat created during operation mainly through on the back side of the reflectors. This minimizes the heat load by about 66 % in the light bundle. Heat-sensitive objects can be brought into the right light as well.

fields.name: Osram halogen bulb G4 HALOSTAR STARLITE 5 W
fields.description:
Warm white LED reflector bulb GU4 MR11 3 W, 190 lumens

The GU4 LED reflector bulb provides a warm white light and requires just 3 watts of power.

fields.name: Philips Hue White Ambiance E27 8.5W, set of 2
fields.description:
Double pack of Philips Hue White Ambiance E27 LED bulbs for control via Bluetooth and ZigBee

With the Hue White Ambiance lamp, every light with a E27 fitting can be turned into a smart device. The practical 2-piece kit is the ideal extension for existing Hue kits. The light can also be directly controlled without bridge/router using the dimmer switch (see the accessories) or with the Philips Hue Bluetooth app for smartphone/tablet thanks to the in-built Bluetooth technology.

The White Ambiance lamp offers the right lighting mood for every situation from relaxation to focused work, since the colour temperature can be selected across a wide range from 2,200 to 6,500 K. These settings can be determined as a program based on your daily routine. Since the light bulb communicates via the ZigBee protocol in addition to Bluetooth, it can be integrated into any smart home system that uses this standard via bridge and router. For example, voice control on site or remote control via a smartphone app becomes possible after integrating Hue.

fields.name: LED bulb B22d 9W, warm white, 806 lumens, set of 4
fields.description:
B22d 9 W LED bulb in a set of four

This set of four provides an economical replacement for four old traditional light bulbs with a power consumption of 60 watts, and doesn’t lose its brightness with a light output of 806 lumens. Thanks to its 100,000 switching cycles, the LED bulb is very robust and another replacement is far in the future.

fields.name: LED bulb filament candle E14 4 W warm white, 3 set
fields.description:
E14 4 W LED filament candle bulb in a set of three

The LED candles in this set of three, which are reminiscent of the original traditional light bulb, offer a strikingly attractive design. At the same time, they offer several advantages: energy efficiency class A++ ensures an economical use, and 100,000 switching cycles show a high level of robustness.
